        public SwitchPlayerServerPayload(java.util.UUID uuid,
                                 java.lang.String name,
                                 java.lang.String server)
        Construct a payload who's purpose is to change a proxied player's server from one to another. It'd be preferred for you to use a UUID, but if you can't (why?) then a username MUST be provided.
        Parameters:
        uuid - the player's UUID
        name - the player's username
        server - the server to switch to
